"     Thomas Levin, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?7/38/7786/contributors\">",
"     C Michael Gibson, MS, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
